{"tid":1570290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「扮獨立」人士特徴一覧","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:56:18.000Z","uid":57405,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de717ff18520e30c99685d153ac80475caa16815","tid":1570290,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"以下為本人所觀察的一些「扮中立」，但實為藍絲的一些共通點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 常強調自己「無黨無派」、「中堅中立」、「不黃不綠」，但之後所說的同藍絲不謀而合。<br />\n<br />\n2. 文宣品多稱自己為「一群熱愛香港的xxx（職業）」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 扮支持示威者，但又與示威者「割蓆」，例如「我其實好支持你地架，不過......」<br />\n<br />\n4. 第一句就話「我強調，我唔係撐警，不過......」<br />\n<br />\n大致上係咁多，如果各位仲發現其他特徵，可以繼續接落去講。"},{"pid":"e84680633560b503c95e511fb9497a362a3e6a54","tid":1570290,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"「其實政府都係衰，不過我地係咪一定要XX呢？」"},{"pid":"d53cd3148ac34da1fddaafe937705d138c45135a","tid":1570290,"uid":297657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"我冇立場，我只係一個小小嘅老百性<br />\n家父日撚日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc6972df820c5d52319e31466a385490850ad29","tid":1570290,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"「我覺得可以冷靜少少，唔一定XX，可以智取。」<br />\n<br />\n「我地全部人未必認同你講既野，但都係同你地一陣線架。」"},{"pid":"7e5eb0febb0c7ee357e64a8792f0c5010be63c27","tid":1570290,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"「大家都係香港人」"},{"pid":"ede0a58d68573fec5898bfd07fc7bfcd732e4af4","tid":1570290,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"請加上數字"},{"pid":"acee580217ce5204328987ecfe5641d19a67dcb0","tid":1570290,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">關於群眾鬥群眾，毛澤東有野想講[長文Must Read]</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569677/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569677/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>「少年，你太年輕年了... 以為搵人打你就叫群眾鬥群眾?」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「等老夫話你知點玩啦!用「特權階級群眾」鬥「無權勢普通群眾」唔係陷阱、係中共治國方針!」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4b306d1d4dfffd156d938de9f7ce29f387f0c40d","tid":1570290,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"「最緊要有唔同聲音，唔可以得一種聲音。」"},{"pid":"dea07c70da5307eb52453868aed87e4febf388ce","tid":1570290,"uid":5067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"唔出力又唔出錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6aa599ca1d10d3387467cf8dff15c9538d0a66","tid":1570290,"uid":30150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"強調自己係中立者當藍論"},{"pid":"373e6c01f0936de05b888bebbd044224ab4fcfb4","tid":1570290,"uid":74076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:31:22.000Z","msg":"政治唔係我地講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965663a003331b6a62b8256e4b84f26d47c38e1d","tid":1570290,"uid":59978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我中立既, 但用暴力呀, 燒野就唔係咁好囉!"},{"pid":"f5ec13c1d1c94d0e3b5626cfb554c5a606364d58","tid":1570290,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"是咪應該扮佢地口吻做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae20d064a6919fd8fb939d65bf76773782099e3","tid":1570290,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係唔公平咖啦...你食飯緊要定自由緊要吖!<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0209c1ef28aa0cb48a913ff2